Ether port of Alchemy archiving tool.

Usage:
arh c archive files...    - create archive of given files
arh t archive             - list contents of archive
arh x archive             - extract archive to current directory
arh h                     - show help message and exit
arh v                     - show arh version and exit

ChangeLog:
[2014-02-19]  Port to libcore 4.0
[2013-02-16]  Port to libcore 3.1
[2012-11-26]  Hard setting rights for archived files
[2012-10-28]  Port to libcore 3.0
[2012-05-31]  Use syntax features available since Alchemy 1.4
[2012-01-23]  Port to libcore 2.0
